{"tid":1348694,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"721 上環開鎗 元朗恐襲","createTime":"2019-07-22T08:43:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T04:43:08.000Z","uid":39552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d7825f9f76eb8c1bc4b6f12b7c42d603691b0d31","tid":1348694,"uid":39552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T08:43:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47af05fa061b664db85484f7a86101d0e1e5129c","tid":1348694,"uid":39552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T08:49:28.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講"},{"pid":"b481c3677b331121ffb5be9a9e08dc3d38de26d0","tid":1348694,"uid":36742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T08:54:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\">721 警黑之夜 - 整合 (上環 + 元朗)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1344541\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1344541</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n[緊急] 上環義士受傷狀況<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1347981\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1347981</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n［整合] 7.21上環開槍清場 有片有圖！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1348209\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1348209</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n721 上環開槍整合<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1348232\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1348232</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n元朗 黑黑相衛 罪狀List，黑材料基地<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1347791\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1347791</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">兩單野係一個局黎，想spin走上環單野！我地要雙軌並行！</span><br />\n721體現警黑合作，香港政權真面目。<br />\n黑警港島三十幾槍，黑社會元朗亂打人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">光復香港，時代革命！\n\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash; 八大訴求 &mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;\n一、徹底撤回修例\n二、收回暴動定義\n三、撤銷對今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪\n四、徹底追究警隊濫權情況\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選\n六、要求永不落實「社會信用評分系統」\n七、要求移除全港「多功能智慧燈柱」\n八、追究元朗鄉黑暴徒及警察失蹤</code></pre>"},{"pid":"0ed609993eb38926ad67ea2664ce16fcbbdfbbc6","tid":1348694,"uid":248470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T08:55:02.000Z","msg":"建制派及其政府 公然向香港市民發動恐怖襲擊！<br />\n<br />\n地鐵故意堅持開住車箱門，任由警黑合作虐打市民<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港政府= 台灣鄭捷"},{"pid":"bfaa421ccb94a6651ca5921f7f8915354e7bdc48","tid":1348694,"uid":39552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:04:26.000Z","msg":"我要律師"},{"pid":"6f2b27df316419050cbc102d4c01a5bc6fe7284c","tid":1348694,"uid":56711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:22:18.000Z","msg":"上環黑警謀殺<br />\n元朗鄉黑恐襲"},{"pid":"b1490536c3215929f64d317ff5066924f1aff8fd","tid":1348694,"uid":39552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:30:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1ab16be1aeb366748d9ba86c9b4953bd0361efb7","tid":1348694,"uid":39552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T04:43:08.000Z","msg":"推"}]}